<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><a name="info01">&nbsp;</a><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司介绍</span></strong></span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 10.9pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">产业类别：</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 36.0pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">橡胶制品制造业</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">产业描述：</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 36.0pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">橡胶制品制造业</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">员　　工：<span style="font-family: verdana, geneva;">150</span>人</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">资 本 额：<span style="font-family: verdana, geneva;">1000</span>万元</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">联 络 人：郭小姐</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">公司地址：台中市大甲区东三街8号</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.104.com.tw/jobbank/custjob/index.php?r=cust&amp;j=386042263846402556583a1d1d1d1d5f24437323189j56"><span style="padding: 0cm; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: #003399; font-family: '新細明體','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm;" lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">地圖</span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt;"><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">电话：04-26820688</span></span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">分機</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">215</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">传真：<span style="font-family: verdana, geneva;">04-26821156</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司网址：</span><a style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 7pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; line-height: 10.65pt;" href="http://www.zon.com.tw/" target="_blank"><span style="padding: 0cm; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: #003399; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm;">http://www.zon.com.tw/</span></a></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 393.85pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a name="info02">&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司简介</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 6.55pt .0001pt 10.9pt;"><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-size: 10pt;">本公司成立于1985年，主要从事橡胶零件设计及各种工业用橡胶产品制造，拥有为数不少的客户群，市场分布于国内与海外。</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 6.55pt .0001pt 10.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">我们拥有优秀的经营团队，整体的营运稳定，获利状况也逐年提升。</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">～欢迎优秀的您一起加入～</span></span></p>
<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a name="info03">&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">主要商品／服务项目</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 6.55pt .0001pt 10.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">橡胶零件设计及专业制造，含O环、垫片、衬套、减震橡胶、防尘套及所有密封件</span></span></p>
<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a name="info04">&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">福利制度</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 6.55pt .0001pt 10.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">劳保/健保/团保</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> <span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">2</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、三节奖金/礼券</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> <span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">3</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、定期健康检查</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> <span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">4</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、年度国内、外旅游/聚餐</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> <span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">5</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、生日蛋糕</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> <span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">6</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、分红奖金</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 6.55pt .0001pt 10.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
